import React from "react";
import tw from "tailwind-styled-components";

const Nav = tw.div`
w-full
h-20
shadow-md
fixed
top-0
left-0

bg-black
text-blue-200
hover:bg-purple-900`;

const Logo = tw.div`
bg-red-400
m-4
w-30
h-14
flex
items-center
justify-center
font-bold
`;
const NavItemWrapper = tw.div`
bg-purple-400
m-4
w-1/2
h-14
flex
items-center
justify-center
`;
const NavItem = tw.h1`
p-1
h-14
flex
items-center
justify-center
`;
const Hamburger = tw.span`
h-14
w-20
float-right
bg-pink-200
`;

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Nav>
      <Logo>WA-HIRED</Logo>
      <NavItemWrapper>
        <NavItem>Home</NavItem>
        <NavItem>Services</NavItem>
        <NavItem>About</NavItem>
        <NavItem>Contact</NavItem>
      </NavItemWrapper>
      <Hamburger></Hamburger>
    </Nav>
  );
};

export default Navbar;
